    </div>

    <div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8f9fa 0%, #e9ecef 100%); padding: 40px; border-radius: 20px; text-align: center; margin-bottom: 50px; box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);">
        <h2 style="font-size: 1.8rem; margin-bottom: 20px; color: #212529;">SoftMarket: Свіжі продукти. Легко та швидко.</h2>
