            </div>

            <div style="flex: 1; min-width: 280px; background: #fff; padding: 30px; border-radius: 15px; border: 1px solid #eee; box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.03);">
                <div style="font-size: 3rem; margin-bottom: 15px;">⚡</div>
